    {
      "theme": "dark",
      "chrome": "none",
      "footer": "none",
      "html": "<div class=\"s1\">\n  <svg class=\"s1__dots\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\">\n    <defs>\n      <pattern id=\"p\" x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"44\" height=\"44\" patternUnits=\"userSpaceOnUse\">\n        <circle cx=\"2\" cy=\"2\" r=\"2\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.10)\"/>\n      </pattern>\n    </defs>\n    <rect width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" fill=\"url(#p)\"/>\n  </svg>\n\n  <div class=\"s1__grid\">\n    <div class=\"s1__kicker\"><span class=\"s1__kickerAccent\"></span> SAVE THIS</div>\n    <div class=\"s1__title\">2026\n창업패키지\n일정표</div>\n    <div class=\"s1__sub\">예비·초기·도약\n접수기간만 한 장 정리</div>\n    <div class=\"s1__badge\">Black / White / Orange</div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
      "css": ".s1{position:absolute;inset:0;background:var(--color-bg-dark);color:#fff;} .s1__dots{position:absolute;inset:0;opacity:.75} .s1__grid{position:relative;z-index:2;height:100%;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:flex-end;padding:120px 88px 120px 88px;gap:28px} .s1__kicker{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;font-size:22px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.18em;color:rgba(255,255,255,.75)} .s1__kickerAccent{display:inline-block;width:48px;height:6px;background:var(--color-accent)} .s1__title{white-space:pre-line;font-size:128px;font-weight:900;line-height:1.02;letter-spacing:-0.06em} .s1__sub{white-space:pre-line;font-size:44px;font-weight:600;line-height:1.35;color:rgba(255,255,255,.78);max-width:860px} .s1__badge{margin-top:18px;align-self:flex-start;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.22);border-radius:999px;padding:12px 20px;font-size:18px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.12em;color:rgba(255,255,255,.65);text-transform:uppercase}"
    },

    {
      "theme": "light",
      "chrome": "full",
      "footer": "minimal",
      "html": "<div class=\"s2\">\n  <div class=\"s2__rule\"></div>\n  <div class=\"s2__title\">통합공고는 \"목록\"\n접수는 \"개별 공고\"</div>\n  <div class=\"s2__body\">연간 통합공고는 안내 성격이에요. 실제 제출·자격·서류는 <span class=\"s2__accent\">사업별 공고</span>를 따라갑니다.</div>\n  <div class=\"s2__pair\">\n    <div class=\"s2__card\">\n      <div class=\"s2__cap\">통합공고</div>\n      <div class=\"s2__big\">연간\n안내</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"s2__card s2__card--accent\">\n      <div class=\"s2__cap\">개별 공고</div>\n      <div class=\"s2__big\">실제\n접수</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"s2__note\">Tip. 제출 직전에는 공고 원문(첨부파일 포함)을 1회 더 확인</div>\n</div>",
      "css": ".s2{height:100%;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;gap:34px} .s2__rule{width:80px;height:8px;background:var(--color-accent)} .s2__title{white-space:pre-line;font-size:96px;font-weight:900;line-height:1.08;letter-spacing:-0.05em;color:var(--color-text-primary);margin:0} .s2__body{font-size:44px;font-weight:600;line-height:1.5;color:var(--color-text-secondary);max-width:880px;word-break:keep-all} .s2__accent{color:var(--color-text-primary);border-bottom:8px solid rgba(255,81,0,.25)} .s2__pair{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:18px;margin-top:6px} .s2__card{background:var(--color-box-bg-light);border:1px solid var(--color-border-light);border-radius:20px;padding:30px 32px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px} .s2__card--accent{border-color:rgba(255,81,0,.35);box-shadow:0 18px 40px rgba(255,81,0,.08)} .s2__cap{font-size:18px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--color-text-secondary)} .s2__big{white-space:pre-line;font-size:64px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-0.04em;line-height:1.06;color:var(--color-text-primary)} .s2__note{margin-top:2px;font-size:28px;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-text-secondary)}"
    },

    {
      "theme": "light",
      "chrome": "full",
      "footer": "minimal",
      "html": "<div class=\"s3\">\n  <div class=\"s3__head\">\n    <div class=\"s3__kicker\">2026 접수 흐름</div>\n    <div class=\"s3__title\">1~3월 타임라인</div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"s3__timeline\">\n    <div class=\"s3__row\">\n      <div class=\"s3__month\">JAN</div>\n      <div class=\"s3__bar\">\n        <div class=\"s3__pill\">도약(딥테크) 01.06~01.27</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"s3__row\">\n      <div class=\"s3__month\">FEB</div>\n      <div class=\"s3__bar\">\n        <div class=\"s3__pill s3__pill--muted\">초기(일반) 01.23~02.13</div>\n        <div class=\"s3__pill s3__pill--muted\">도약(일반) 01.23~02.13</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"s3__row\">\n      <div class=\"s3__month\">MAR</div>\n      <div class=\"s3__bar\">\n        <div class=\"s3__pill\">예비(수정) 03.06~03.24</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"s3__foot\">* 일정은 변경될 수 있어요. 제출 직전 원문을 재확인하세요.</div>\n</div>",
      "css": ".s3{height:100%;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;gap:42px} .s3__kicker{font-size:18px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--color-accent)} .s3__title{font-size:92px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-0.05em;line-height:1.06;color:var(--color-text-primary)} .s3__timeline{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:26px;margin-top:6px} .s3__row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:120px 1fr;gap:22px;align-items:start} .s3__month{font-size:22px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:.16em;color:var(--color-text-secondary);padding-top:10px} .s3__bar{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px} .s3__pill{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;align-self:flex-start;background:rgba(255,81,0,.10);border:1px solid rgba(255,81,0,.22);color:var(--color-text-primary);border-radius:999px;padding:16px 22px;font-size:30px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-0.01em} .s3__pill--muted{background:var(--color-box-bg-light);border-color:var(--color-border-light);color:var(--color-text-primary)} .s3__foot{font-size:26px;font-weight:600;color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-top:8px}"
